---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Contribute to Pulsar OS">
    <section class="contribute-hero">
        <div
            class="container"
            style="text-align: center; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;"
        >
            <h1 class="section-title">Contribute to Pulsar OS</h1>
            <p class="section-subtitle" style="margin-bottom: 40px;">
                Pulsar OS is an open source project built by and for the
                community. There are many ways to get involved, whether you're a
                developer, designer, translator, documentation writer, or simply
                want to help out.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="contribute-ways">
        <div class="container" style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
            <div class="community-card" style="margin-bottom: 32px;">
                <h2 class="community-title" style="font-size: 1.75rem;">
                    GitHub Organization
                </h2>
                <p class="community-desc">
                    All of Pulsar OS source code is available on GitHub. You can
                    explore the repositories, open issues, send pull requests
                    and follow development in real time. The project is
                    organized using a project board where you can see which
                    tasks are pending, in progress or completed.
                </p>
                <div class="community-actions">
                    <a
                        href="https://github.com/Inled-Pulsar-OS"
                        target="_blank"
                        rel="noopener noreferrer"
                        class="btn btn-primary"
                    >
                        GitHub Organization
                    </a>
                    <a
                        href="https://github.com/orgs/Inled-Pulsar-OS/projects/1"
                        target="_blank"
                        rel="noopener noreferrer"
                        class="btn btn-secondary"
                    >
                        Project Board
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="community-card" style="margin-bottom: 32px;">
                <h2 class="community-title" style="font-size: 1.75rem;">
                    Matrix Chat
                </h2>
                <p class="community-desc">
                    We're planning to set up a Matrix server for fast
                    communication. Also we have in mind to set up both Telegram
                    and Discord communities that are going to be redirected to
                    the Matrix server and viceversa.
                </p>
                <div class="community-actions">
                    <a
                        href="#"
                        class="btn btn-primary"
                        style="opacity: 0.6; cursor: not-allowed;"
                    >
                        Discord (coming soon)
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="community-card" style="margin-bottom: 32px;">
                <h2 class="community-title" style="font-size: 1.75rem;">
                    AI-assisted development policy
                </h2>
                <p class="community-desc">
                    We welcome pull requests developed with the help of AI
                    assistants, as long as they meet the following requirements:
                </p>
                <div style="text-align: left; max-width: 650px; margin: 0 auto 32px auto; color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.6;">
                    <ol style="padding-left: 20px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px;">
                        <li>
                            <strong>Testing:</strong> Every AI-generated PR must
                            pass the appropriate testing before being submitted.
                            We don't accept untested code.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Bilingual comments:</strong> All comments in
                            the code must be written in both English and Spanish
                            so the codebase remains accessible to our community.
                            AI tools handle this effortlessly.
                        </li>
                    </ol>
                </div>
                <p class="community-desc" style="margin-bottom: 0;">
                    AI is a powerful productivity tool, not a replacement for
                    responsibility. If your PR is well tested and properly
                    documented, it will be reviewed like any other.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="community-card">
                <h2 class="community-title" style="font-size: 1.75rem;">
                    Other ways to contribute
                </h2>
                <p class="community-desc">
                    You don't need to be a programmer to help. You can
                    contribute with documentation, translations, graphic design,
                    bug reports, or simply by sharing Pulsar OS with others.
                    Every bit helps.
                </p>
                <div class="community-actions">
                    <a
                        href="https://github.com/Inled-Pulsar-OS"
                        target="_blank"
                        rel="noopener noreferrer"
                        class="btn btn-secondary"
                    >
                        Explore repositories
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="contribute-back">
        <div class="container" style="text-align: center; padding: 60px 0;">
            <a href="/" class="btn btn-secondary">&larr; Back to landing</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <style>
        .contribute-hero {
            padding: 140px 0 60px 0;
        }

        .contribute-ways {
            padding: 0 0 40px 0;
        }

        .contribute-back {
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        }

        .community-card {
            background-color: var(--bg-card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            border-radius: 32px;
            padding: 60px 48px;
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
    </style>
</Layout>
